              NOTE:

Sequel to the Prequel is the third album from Babyshambles, fronted by Pete Doherty. It was recorded at Question Du Son, Paris and mixed in The Bunker, London, with producer/mixer and long time 'Shambles collaborator Stephen Street. The sleeve artwork is by Brit-art icon Damien Hirst.
